{"tid":1723141,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警告：最新五毛公關技倆","createTime":"2019-11-15T06:00:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T06:48:04.000Z","uid":73026,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6ece4583145c73c4365d691f0f8968903b373706","tid":1723141,"uid":73026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:00:55.000Z","msg":"就係行返以前個套，賣慘情<br />\n<br />\n1／浸會醫院塞撚住左好撚慘，睇唔到醫生<br />\n2／返唔到工好撚慘，手停口停<br />\n<br />\n自己提醒返自己呢幾個月發生過d<br />\n1／夠唔夠幾百個手足死得不明不白慘？<br />\n2／夠唔夠比狗強姦既女手足慘？<br />\n3／夠唔夠比狗告要坐幾年既手足慘？<br />\n4／夠唔夠比狗射爆眼，比黑社會斬手斬腳，割頸插肚既手足慘？<br />\n<br />\n唔該記住呢幾個月個政府同班狗有幾咁仆街<br />\n見到再有呢d打慘情牌既post／人唔該叫佢地同政府講，唔撚好同我地手足講<br />\n<br />\n仲有就係另一班區選撚，乜撚野等區選過埋先。唔洗多講，呢幾個月有好多同類既風向，我唔係話區選冇撚用，而係區選只係支線中既支線。唔撚會係為左個區選而放棄依家大家既momentum。<br />\n<br />\n最後祝大家武運昌隆，黎緊星期五六同下個禮拜靠哂大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"569f2781c994c5c3d10b9d6a17290854a7547a65","tid":1723141,"uid":73026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:03:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0ea26bf75512766bd01f87e7431adc5bbd61cbe9","tid":1723141,"uid":51618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:03:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72a6e52074cc908d5df7fbfd649383ed69d57dd7","tid":1723141,"uid":55384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:04:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a8bc478ec7df8516f55fa74a24af3d0175175e4","tid":1723141,"uid":281756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:05:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24815a001a4a41ca99c177473331fddfffe3283d","tid":1723141,"uid":281756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:05:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf0f6f06754168e3c817564dd29a52637774e75","tid":1723141,"uid":73026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:08:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee41514ead63e2cb717ea8edd26c1fd9987013c","tid":1723141,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:10:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e627f396dce3b7b3fb4812ab0ff8317fcb1574a","tid":1723141,"uid":60321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:15:56.000Z","msg":"香港人醒目少少呀，最後機會喇 <br />\n<br />\n五毛網上扮偏激既留言你阻唔到，你越反感佢越留多幾個。<br />\n現實黑警混入扮示威者，做你唔認同既行為嫁禍比你，你又阻唔到，你越反感佢越做多幾單。<br />\n<br />\n事實係你越比反應，越加把口去拗，就越中分化計<br />\n只有你繼續做你認為啱既行動，講你認為有建設性既野<br />\n去洗走唔真實既行為同言論，令合理既現論同行為繼續佔有絕對主流比例，咁先有意思<br />\n<br />\n所以每次越係面對分化，你就要愈係出多分力去做正確野<br />\n其他有咩唔認同既野，等贏左先再計"},{"pid":"d9efff6afab5bc12e4ba1f7c59a563a3b5258a14","tid":1723141,"uid":73026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:48:04.000Z","msg":"PUSH"}]}